Oracle Auditing Tools by patrik@cqure.net
-----------------------------------------

Requirements
------------
Oracle JDBC driver, which can be obtained at www.oracle.com or
simply by searching the internet with eg. google for classess111.zip.

Unix
----
Modify the path to the java binary in the .sh files.
Modify the path to the JDBC driver, normaly:

<ORACLE_HOME>/jdbc/lib/classes111.zip
or
<ORACLE_HOME>/jdbc/lib/classes12.zip

Windows
-------
Modify the path to the java binary in the .bat files.
Modify the path to the JDBC driver, normaly:

<ORACLE_HOME>\jdbc\lib\classes111.zip
or
<ORACLE_HOME>\jdbc\lib\classes12.zip

Patrik Karlsson, http://www.cqure.net